---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Us">
	<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 max-w-4xl">
		<div class="mb-12">
			<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-center md:text-left">About Greek Nation</h1>
			<p class="text-xl text-zinc-300 font-light leading-relaxed">
				Greek Nation was built to put artists and Greek organizations in direct contact — no agency in the middle deciding who performs where.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="space-y-12">
			<section class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
				<p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					For too long, booking an artist for a campus event meant going through multiple layers of management, agencies, and middlemen. We created Greek Nation to streamline that process. We empower Greek organizations to browse top-tier talent and submit direct offers, putting the power of a performance back in the hands of the creators and the organizations that host them.
				</p>
				<p class="text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed">
					Whether it's a huge EDM show, a massive tailgate, or a formal, we're here to make the connection simple and transparent.
				</p>
			</section>

			<section class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Direct Booking</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">Cut out the gatekeepers. Connect directly with management and artists.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-800 rounded-2xl p-8 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Built for Greek Life</h3>
					<p class="text-zinc-400 text-sm">A platform specifically tailored to the unique needs and energy of Greek organizations.</p>
				</div>
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
